For create database with attached users:

  ./create-db-user.sh app1

First run with full access root:

  ./mongosh.sh root

For list of databases:

  db.adminCommand({ listDatabases:1 })

For list of users:

  use admin;
  db.system.users.find();

For change user password:

  use yourDbName
  db.changeUserPassword("username", "newPassword")
  // or
  db.changeUserPassword("username", passwordPrompt())

You can generate random password

  tr -dc A-Za-z0-9 </dev/urandom | head -c 48 ; echo ''
